Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:14.47,On Top,,0,0,0,,"-1 day before-"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I somehow ended up back here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.22,0:00:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did we have to become second-years?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Down below, Shimamura and our\Nnew classmates are having PE class.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.57,0:00:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Shimamura even realize I'm up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I realized it, Shimamura\Nwas surrounded by new people,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.45,0:00:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and things were going well for her,\Nbut not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,To put it simply, that's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.54,0:00:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura was smiling...\Nwith people she barely knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.47,0:00:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And I couldn't find a difference in\Nthat smile with the one she showed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.01,0:01:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It frustrated me, I couldn't breathe,\Nand I felt like crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.22,0:01:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that there was never\Nanything actually dramatic or special
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,between Shimamura and I?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.24,0:01:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she a third-year?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,As she sat a little further down,\Nshe started to read her book quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This calm takes over the area
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and I lose my place even here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for taking your spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually knew that Shimamura\Nwould never show up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura and I aren't alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason we even met in\Nthe gym was because I'm alone
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:04:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and Shimamura was bored and left class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I realized it, I ended up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What I ended up remembering\Nwere precious times with Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so boring. Everything's so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so boring without Shimamura around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Shimamura would like something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I looking for something\NShimamura might like even now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.41,0:04:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey. I think you dropped this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... Yeah, I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it was that important.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never been interested in stuff like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but if I had a matching one with Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:06:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... Why am I crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This was basically a mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm the same\Nas that puppy on display.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I pretty much put myself in that case
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and instead of being able to attract customers,\NI'm just sitting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:25.09,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Money, marriage, relationships,\NI'll predict it all!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go home with troubles in your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll never be able to welcome\Na wonderful tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Are you a fortuneteller?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, or perhaps, a fortunegiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you anything you need to know. Even...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...the reason behind those tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.91,0:07:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply put...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be having romance troubles!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be 1,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here's--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks kindly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then. Let me just ask you one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that person have longer hair than you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That person?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.56,0:07:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The one that's very dear to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura's hair... is so smooth\Nand pretty... and soft...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're already lost in thought,\NI think I got the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, what you are lacking...\Nis enthusiasm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You were worried about how\Nothers view you and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very obvious what you're lacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you a very simple way\Nyou can gain enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Face that direction and scream.\NRight here, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't, you'll just waste your 1,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But if this is what you truly wish for...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, do I really have to do it\Nright here and now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it, if you don't want to have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, scream! Scream everything\Nyou're feeling with all your might!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw your arms up and declare it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only way you're going to be able\Nto embrace and steel your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Your voice is too soft and\Nthat wasn't the best line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And you didn't throw up your arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're thinking, "If I had the guts to do that,\NI wouldn't have this issue."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, this whole issue\Nwould be resolved if you had guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm gonna do my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're clearly not. Now, one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to have any regrets, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you mustn't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I can't seem to get over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I ended up just denying how I felt\Nand just ran away from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I'd just stopped and\Nactually talked to Shimamura,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.81,0:09:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,none of this would've happened.\NA part of me regretted that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, excellent. Now, one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.71,0:09:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you actually did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:10:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,People don't need to know the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They need to strongly desire the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, thanks, I--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if you'll excuse me.\NMay you have a bright future!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.15,0:10:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.57,0:10:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the weekend is over, I'll tell Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Or so I told myself and actually came\Nto school, but still, I ended up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:32.09,On Top,,0,0,0,,"{\i1}Thunderheads and Rain{\i0}\NEiji Kikkawa"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This book...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for taking your spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:39.30,On Top,,0,0,0,,"{\i1}Thunderheads and Rain{\i0}\NEiji Kikkawa"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.76,0:10:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"Why did I keep running? Because I was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I spend every day afraid thinking about
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,what if my tomorrow becomes\Nyesterday to the rest of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,as I waste time hesitating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to be left behind because of\Nsome great change I don't know about,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather run to the front and choose a path\Nwhere I can make the change myself."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Left behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.79,0:11:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a second-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Only Shimamura was able\Nto become a second-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura is in class right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She's eating lunch. She's not coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason she would.\NOkay, I've got to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Being in a club is sort of a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no room\Nin the place I want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:42.32,On Top,,0,0,0,,They're so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:44.14,On Top,,0,0,0,,Relationships are so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:45.80,On Top,,0,0,0,,You can say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll just have to make room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:49.08,On Top,,0,0,0,,By the way, on our way home,\Nwanna get pancakes again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Shi--?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was my official start\Nas a second-year in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.52,0:12:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how long it'd been\Nsince I heard Adachi's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this was the first time\Nin this classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I sit next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh, let me get you a seat...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Shimamura. I bought some breads.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? This many? Isn't this a bit much?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.34,0:12:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have whichever one you want, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll take one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll have the jam bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.07,0:13:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, I can't eat that many.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a little embarrassing,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think she made up her mind\Nthat I'm the only one she needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder about me, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There are times if I even really need anyone,\Nand I still don't have an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What I did know was my flimsy relationship\Nwith Sancho and the others
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,would fade away even before\Nwe changed seats again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, let's go home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.61,0:13:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.28,0:13:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you just teasing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That strap...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these popular right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.63,0:14:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you buy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was thinking of getting one, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'd be matching...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So if Adachi got one, she'd be\Nmatching with me and Tarumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.95,0:14:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, can I hold your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does everyone want to\Nhold my hand so badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they all think I'm going\Nto wander off somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.43,0:14:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,\NTarumi takes my left hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but Adachi takes my right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Adachi. I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:15:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got your bike, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see each other tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're coming to school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I want to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't actually go home\Nunless you let go of my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're not going anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going anywhere. Nope, nope, nope...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... She reminds me of a sad little puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Come here a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uh, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.17,0:16:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I think you're the best, Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, where did this... uh, hug come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We hadn't done anything in a while, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Done anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you were with those other girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you were jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Adachi not only want me\Nto be her big sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but also her mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If Sancho and the others saw us right now,\Nthey'd really get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:17:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've gotta get home, little Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you treating me like a little kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.64,0:17:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, can I call you later?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me? Sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call you... around seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.37,0:17:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But I eat dinner around seven...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, if it isn't Shimamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like some strawberry shortcake?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.89,0:17:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But where did you guys get money for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I think Yachi pulled this cake\Nout of her pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.56,0:17:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Praise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I have decided to become Yashiemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.11,0:17:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yashiemon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:18:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's anything you'd like,\NShimamura, just--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home. Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we have dinner earlier? I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm making dinner right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, would you like some sweet crackers?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.34,0:18:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, where did you get those?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I am Yashiemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to eat earlier\Nthan everyone else then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. What's for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.64,0:18:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakitori I just bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you chopping it up like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.03,0:18:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing Adachi, she'll probably\Ncall me right at seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she's sitting very rigidly\Nin front of her phone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:56.05,On Top,,0,0,0,,"4/21 (Tue)"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:57.55,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Adachi Incoming Call"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:19:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And here we go. Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.59,0:19:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening. Are your legs asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.44,0:19:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just a guess. So, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.86,0:19:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.74,0:19:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured you wanted to talk about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.03,0:19:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hadn't called you for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to make any friends, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.83,0:19:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"And"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.05,0:19:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have you, Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Adachi always talk like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you talk to anyone else\Non the phone, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.48,0:19:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah. Sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.06,0:19:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.94,0:19:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you sound so sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:20:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I thought I was the only one...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one that I call, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to just end the call?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.34,0:20:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if we're not going to talk,\Nit's sort of a waste of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not at all! I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Because then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Because then...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.18,0:20:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,While I'm on the phone with you,\NI get to have your time all to myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a bit possessive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I-I think it's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:20:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is totally normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:21:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,in the end, it's not a bad feeling\Nknowing that someone cares about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.15,0:21:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Adachi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:27.66,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Shimamura In Call"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.91,0:21:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Himamuwa... You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.71,0:21:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm with Adachi,\Nmy possibilities are fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.17,0:21:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had to choose someone\Nto walk alongside with...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.47,0:21:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The choices get narrowed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.36,0:22:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I should choose whatever's best for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.07,0:22:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears that Adachi has chosen the path\Nwhere she doesn't need anyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.33,0:22:22.05,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 11: 'The Moon and Determination,\NDetermination and Friends'"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.01,0:24:07.00,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Next Time: 'Friends and Love,\NLove and Cherry Blossoms'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.03,0:23:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Adashimapedia: The final episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.12,0:23:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I've realized something insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.07,0:23:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.62,0:24:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If we never air the next episode,\Nthe final episode will never come!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.91,0:24:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning this anime will never end!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.92,0:24:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty sure people will just think\Nit got canceled then.
